,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"世界變，現在高學歷正正常常都唔係容易搵工<br />\n唔考慮體力勞動、唔考慮技術型專業<br />\n只想嘆冷氣坐辦公室真係唔容易"},{"pid":"4e936487bb00afa0c805e7750ac0c88aeb6b6ed0","tid":714301,"uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"香港大把大專生   點解要請你先"},{"pid":"0fe2bf38fd068d6a9757d016f5870cb18931f988","tid":714301,"uid":87339,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"d92a17832626ad500fbae99be3584f1c2ff6b856","tid":714301,"uid":51469,"like":471,"dislike":4,"score":467,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"經濟犯罪想做會計......"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"呢d先係人才<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e839a3a20be4704a6dfc2d7e86626e9f0387a702","tid":714301,"uid":8410,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:07:48.000Z","msg":"如果同外國比，外國高學歷出到黎搵到收銀做都已經好難得，好多都唔會請"},{"pid":"f31ded6fbf3b244b7a46a99e158a6274d4a55771","tid":714301,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:09:58.000Z","msg":"衰乜要坐五年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2ee764ecaf1a8819cd7fc09f70e4e4cf4dda0f","tid":714301,"uid":164913,"like":29,"dislike":24,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d98df8a353a9b99292f8c917e04ad6afe401b2ac","tid":714301,"uid":141033,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"搞技能性啲嘅職業訓練最好，例如廚師、髮型師、按摩技師呢類，搞個廉價餐廳/髮型屋/按摩中心俾佢哋實習吓，收嗰少少錢咪俾懲教圍皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42eca2207ebe88fa411aeee1b8b0da33c0fe6a72","tid":714301,"uid":47359,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"bb2ee764ecaf1a8819cd7fc09f70e4e4cf4dda0f","tid":714301,"uid":164913,"like":29,"dislike":24,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被